original_title: T.O.H.C. LIVE 2017 (60 Minutes Of Hardcore Punk Shows)
overview: A compilation of various hardcore punk shows from the city of Toronto.  Filmed by youtuber PNG with various shots from the venues: Soybomb, Faith/Void, The Silver Dollar Room and Ozzys.  With performances by Career Suicide, The Brain, Prom Nite, VCR and many many more.
tagline: TOHC LIVE (50 Minutes of Toronto Hardcore Punk Shows)
title: T.O.H.C. LIVE 2017 (60 Minutes Of Hardcore Punk Shows)
